<H1 ALIGN="CENTER">Handicrafts of Varanasi</H1>
        
		Varanasi has, since times immemorial, been hailed
        as a leading center for some of the finest Indian handicrafts. The most
        renowned craft of Varanasi city is silk weaving. 'Banarasi Sarees',
        produced by local craftsman are among the most preferred, not only in
        India but also all over the world. Besides the famous Benarasi Sari,
        brassware, copperware, ivory work, glass bangles, wood, stone and clay
        toys and exquisite gold jewellery are some of the other crafts Varanasi
        city is famous for. Among the other shopping attractions of Varanasi and
        surrounding areas are the Bhadohi Carpets and musical instruments.



